  "top10": {
    "introHtml": "<p>Top 10 picks for a cheap fun second car near Media, PA (ZIP 19063) \u2014 ranked by condition, reliability, and fun factor. Sources: AutoTrader page 1 (26 of 64 local listings). Cars.com and CarGurus required Chrome JS rendering unavailable this run.</p>",
