        "url": "https://www.autotrader.com/cars-for-sale/vehicle/754834213",
        "whyGood": "A 2015 435i xDrive Convertible for $8,500 is an objectively absurd value \u2014 this car listed for $58K new. The N55 turbocharged 3.0L inline-6 makes 300hp and the xDrive AWD is genuinely useful in PA winters. Clean title via Private Seller Exchange. High miles (140K) is the only real knock.",
